Package com.cloudera.director.spi.v1.model.exception

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PluginExceptionCondition
    Represents an error or warning that contributed to an exception.
    PluginExceptionConditionAccumulator
    Accumulator for plugin exception conditions.
    PluginExceptionDetails
    Provides additional exception details to enable better UI feedback when exceptions occur.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PluginExceptionCondition.Type
    The type of condition.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AbstractPluginException
    Abstract base class for plugin exceptions.
    InvalidCredentialsException
    Used to signal that supplied credential information does not allow successful authentication.
    TransientProviderException
    Represents a failure interacting with the cloud provider (such as a temporary network outage) that might be overcome by retrying the operation.
    UnrecoverableProviderException
    Represents a failure interacting with the cloud provider that is unlikely to be overcome by retrying the operation.
    ValidationException
    Represents a configuration validation failure.
